A Lego nursery is the stuff children's dreams are made of and these babies are sure to fit right in.

The special tank has built especially for four baby bamboo sharks who have now taken up residence in their new home.

The unique aquarium at Legoland Windsor has been kitted out by model makers with brightly coloured Duplo trains and bridges for the sharks to swim through.

